text: Nawaf Ahmed (born 17 February 1992) is a Kuwaiti cricketer who plays for the Kuwait national cricket team. In July 2019, he was named in Kuwait's Twenty20 International (T20I) squad for the Regional Finals of the 2018–19 ICC T20 World Cup Asia Qualifier tournament. He made his T20I debut for Kuwait against Malaysia on 22 July 2019. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Kuwaiti cricketers Category:Kuwait Twenty20 International cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
